title: LCD Writing Tablet 8.5 inch Electronic Writing Drawing Doodle Board Handwriting Paper Drawing Draft Pad with Smart Stylus and Lock Button for Kids and Adults
description:
• About Product:-

  • LCD drawing tablet use flexible liquid crystal technology, depends on the pressure sensing to display text, pictures and graphics.
  • No paper and no eraser, just press the erase button, the graphics tablets will be cleaned, it can be erased over tens of thousands times.



  • Built-in smart stylus, easy to write and draw, you can use any writing object even your nails to write on this LCD draft board.
  • The durable electronic drawing board. High quality design, long using life and no needed to charge.
  • Save paper and tree, good protection for the nature. LCD writing board.
  • Ultra-thin and lightweight, only 0.19-inch thickness and 2.8 oz.

1. The tablet's writing surface creates lines of different thickness based on how hard you push.

2. Please don’t write on the LCD area with sharp objects.

3. Please don’t bend this electronic notepad and Do not soak in the water and any liquid.

4. Do not placed it at above high temperature 50℃ and under low temperature 0℃.

A great bridge to increase parent-child attachment.

  • Teach children to know letters and pictures
  • Let parents see the child's rich imagination

A good tool to motivate children to be creative

  • imagination dance on it
  • Cultivate friendships by creating together
